  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6264491/" class="title-link">爱情不能承受的时代之重----评《1980年代的爱情》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6264491"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3085350/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3085350-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3085350/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">林间的猴子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-06"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-06 01:13:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6264491_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  尝有好奇地思忖爱情小说与言情的区别，多时的无解后终于给出了自己如下的答案：言情小说通过一系列跌宕起伏的剧情的刻画表现单纯的爱恋本身；而爱情小说则是通过爱、往往还是非常平淡的爱情的叙述反应时代的沧桑与生活的苦乐。如此说来，爱情小说就超越了其顾名思义的爱与故事...

