              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28596574/" class="">第147页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59995660/" class=" " title="DreamZ">DreamZ</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28596574">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">一座城池对于一个人的意义，很多时候，仅仅是因为那城里住着某个你牵情的人。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-16 14:53</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">15人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                一座城池对于一个人的意义，很多时候，仅仅是因为那城里住着某个你牵情的人。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28596574/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
