      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="28526605">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59995660/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u59995660-1.jpg" alt="DreamZ" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28526605/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28526605/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59995660/" class=" " title="DreamZ">DreamZ</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28526605">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">她的面庞隐居在日光背后，只有性感的声音翻越了那些窗棂构成的光柱，散漫地抚摸着我的耳朵。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-11 10:11</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                她的面庞隐居在日光背后，只有性感的声音翻越了那些窗棂构成的光柱，散漫地抚摸着我的耳朵。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







